TESTER detected test failures:

## Failed Tests
- Missing CSS file: css/stats.css (referenced in index.html:27)
- Missing CSS file: css/responsive.css (referenced in index.html:32)

## Error Output
```
FILE VALIDATION RESULTS:
[OK] reset.css
[OK] variables.css
[OK] fonts.css
[OK] icons.css
[OK] animations.css
[OK] header.css
[OK] hero.css
[OK] search.css
[OK] roster.css
[OK] statistics-counter.css
[OK] gallery.css
[MISSING] stats.css
[OK] timeline.css
[OK] threat-level.css
[OK] faq.css
