## Suspected Cause
The main branch index.html references two CSS files that do not exist in the css/ directory:

1. **css/stats.css** (line 27) - Required for styling the Operational Dashboard section (lines 357-399 in index.html)
   - Elements requiring styles: `.stats__container`, `.stats__title`, `.stats__grid`, `.stats__card` variants
   - Card types: --missions, --team, --alerts, --response, --success, --resources
   - Sub-elements: `.stats__icon`, `.stats__number`, `.stats__label`, `.stats__sparkline` variants

2. **css/responsive.css** (line 32) - Required for responsive media queries (mobile/tablet breakpoints)
   - Breakpoints needed: 1024px (small desktop), 768px (tablet), 480px (mobile)
   - Sections requiring responsive styles: header nav, roster grid, stats grid, gallery grid, footer layout

**Impact:**
- **Browser 404 errors** - 2 failed CSS file requests on every page load
- **Broken stats dashboard** - Operational Dashboard section renders unstyled
- **No responsive design** - Site layout breaks on mobile/tablet devices
- **Poor UX** - Non-functional on screens below 1024px width

## Suggested Fix

**Option 1: Create Missing Files** (Recommended)

1. **Create css/stats.css:**
```css
.stats__container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
}

.stats__title {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  color: var(--primary-color);
}

.stats__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
}

.stats__card {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.stats__card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.stats__icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.stats__number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent-color); }
.stats__label { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; }

/* Card variants */
.stats__card--missions { border-left: 4px solid #00bcd4; }
.stats__card--team { border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; }
.stats__card--alerts { border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; }
.stats__card--response { border-left: 4px solid #9c27b0; }
.stats__card--success { border-left: 4px solid #8bc34a; }
.stats__card--resources { border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; }

/* Sparklines */
.stats__sparkline {
  height: 40px;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, var(--sparkline-color) 100%);
  border-radius: 4px;
}
```

2. **Create css/responsive.css:**
```css
/* Desktop Small */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .stats__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

/* Tablet */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .roster__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .stats__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .gallery__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .header__nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .footer__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .roster__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .gallery__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .footer__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero__title { font-size: 2rem; }
  .stats__title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
  .header__container { padding: 1rem; }
}
```

**Option 2: Remove References** (Quick fix, not recommended)
- Remove lines 27 and 32 from index.html
- Results in unstyled stats section and non-responsive site

**Investigation Steps:**
```bash
git log --all --full-history -- css/stats.css css/responsive.css
git log --oneline -10 -- index.html
git blame index.html | grep -E 'stats\.css|responsive\.css'
```

