## Error Output
```
CSS File Validation: FAILED

Referenced in index.html but NOT FOUND:
  - css/search-bar.css (line 23)
  - css/stats.css (line 28)
  - css/responsive.css (line 33)

Existing CSS files (25 total):
  reset.css, variables.css, fonts.css, icons.css, animations.css
  header.css, hero.css, search.css, roster.css, statistics-counter.css
