```

## Suspected Cause
The main branch index.html references three CSS files that do not exist:

1. **css/search-bar.css** (line 23) - Required for compact search bar in header (index.html:57-61)
   - Elements: `.search-bar--compact`, `.search-bar__icon`, `.search-bar__input`, `.search-bar__clear`

2. **css/stats.css** (line 28) - Required for Operational Dashboard section (index.html:368-410)
   - Elements: `.stats__container`, `.stats__grid`, `.stats__card` variants, `.stats__sparkline`

3. **css/responsive.css** (line 33) - Required for responsive media queries
   - Breakpoints: 1024px, 768px, 480px

**Impact:**
- **3 browser 404 errors** on every page load
- **Unstyled header search bar** - No styling for compact search in header
- **Broken stats dashboard** - Operational Dashboard renders without styles
- **No responsive design** - Site breaks on mobile/tablet

## Suggested Fix

**Create Missing CSS Files:**

1. **css/search-bar.css:**
```css
.search-bar--compact {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}

.search-bar--compact:focus-within {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent-color);
}

.search-bar__icon {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

.search-bar__input {
  border: none;
  background: transparent;
  color: inherit;
  outline: none;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  width: 200px;
}

.search-bar__clear {
  border: none;
  background: transparent;
  color: inherit;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0.7;
  transition: opacity 0.3s;
}

.search-bar__clear:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}
```

2. **css/stats.css:** (Same as previous reports)

3. **css/responsive.css:** (Same as previous reports)

**Investigation:**
```bash
git log --all -- css/search-bar.css css/stats.css css/responsive.css
git blame index.html | grep -E 'search-bar\.css|stats\.css|responsive\.css'
```
